---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="Top AI Search Agencies UK 2026 | Rank4AI" description="The top AI search agencies in the UK for 2026. Ranked on methodology, platform coverage and results.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Research', href: '/research/' },
      { label: 'Rankings', href: '/research/rankings/' },
      { label: 'Top AI Search Agencies UK 2026' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag mt-6">Rankings</p>
    <h1 class="mb-4">Top AI Search Agencies UK 2026</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Updated April 2026</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">AI search agencies help businesses get recommended by ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI. This ranking covers the UK agencies with genuine AI search capability - not SEO agencies adding a buzzword.</p>

    <img src="/images/content/ai-search-signals.svg" alt="AI search visibility" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-10" loading="lazy">

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="card-teal-border">
        <h2 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2">Rank4AI</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-2">UK AI search agency working exclusively on AI search visibility. Proprietary Five Signal Model. Tests all six AI platforms. Original research from 1,400+ UK business audits. Ecosystem services from GBP 800/mo.</p>
