        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">rank4ai.co.uk</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2">AwarenessAI</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-2">AI visibility monitoring platform with agency services. Dashboard product for ongoing tracking. Transparent pricing from GBP 100/mo for monitoring.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted">awarenessai.co.uk</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2">Varn</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-2">Specialist SEO and GEO agency. 15+ years in search. Google Premier Partner. Dedicated AI Visibility Framework and innovation team.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted">varn.co.uk</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2">Found</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-2">AI-first Everysearch agency with proprietary Luminr technology. Large agency resources covering SEO, PPC and AI search. London based.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted">found.co.uk</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2">Buried Agency</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-2">Bristol-based GEO and SEO agency. Entity clarity and content architecture focus. Early mover in the UK GEO space.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted">buriedagency.com</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related Rankings</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <a href="/research/rankings/top-ai-seo-agencies-uk-2026/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Top 10 AI SEO Agencies UK 2026</span></a>
        <a href="/research/rankings/best-ai-search-audits-uk/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Best AI Search Audits UK</span></a>
        <a href="/research/rankings/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Rankings</span></a>
